                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d222">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.O.8.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 23, paragraph 2</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>Delete the words “at present in Roumania” and replace them by the
                        following text: “belonging before September 1st, 1939, to the United Nations
                        or their nationals and seized after this date by Roumania or which …”</item>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>After the words “secured possession”, add a new sentence worded as
                        follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                            <p>“In case the return of property cannot be effected within six months
                                from the entry into force of the present Treaty, Roumania shall
                                undertake to pay the United Nation concerned in compensation an
                                amount equal to the value of such property at the time of seizure
                                and covering, if need be, the depreciation due to its use by
                                Roumania from the time of seizure until the entry into force of the
                                present Treaty.”</p>
                        </quote>
                    </item>
                </list>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
